Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get a good rest on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look so out of it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should fix yourself up for the event, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still brooding over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your break-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:42.76,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,In truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:51.53,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't have any regrets now about getting dumped.{anymore seemed clunky to me, but I am willing to bargain.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:03:01.32,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?{cf. e01, 11:00.93}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.60,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terrible at getting the gist of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and then I fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,...but usually I'm pretty calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do about today's after-party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chief said it's on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made a promise today so I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie. I'm watching a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it with Nanoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. She forced me to promise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You just go and drink with the chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the other day, after we had a meeting here, weren't you flirting with a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flirting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I-Idiot! N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Nanoka, wasn't it?{hmmmmmm}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just say she was your sister in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri, help me carry these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by, "flirting with Nanoka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stare at me like it's that unusual.{unusual is kinda clunk---vocabulary failing me}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a beard this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to look clean for our events, or we'll get scolded.{"clean up" instead of "look clean"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This movie is...{ellipsis unnecessary? replace with what}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you spacing out?{because prepositions is bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me your student ID.{herpaderpa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy the tickets.{retard mode, engage!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking, making you come home all alone at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said, "it doesn't matter; just go home first".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went off somewhere right after the movie ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did that bum go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your uniform's going to get wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I ever told you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's my younger sister whom I've been living apart from until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know my parents are divorced, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been with my mom the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We started living together this spring because her high school is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you had something to tell me, so I was wondering what it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to think I started going after high school girls since getting dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just so like you, to be worried about appearances while dating high school girls.{idk if im doin it rite}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:50.62,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a foolish thought passed through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:57.75,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,"That's right; it's been three months since I last had sex".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.89,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But it's fine, because you can drink!{two distinct phrases?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.09,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It is! You're way stronger than me!{"stronger", hmm}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:56.42,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,{sou ka na?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my favorite restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I come here often by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.85,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.74,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.82,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't joke around about things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.62,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,How about Sachiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.63,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,She's just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.77,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.30,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...{ellipsis-abuse-raeg}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's work been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used to always tell me that you wanted to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who could forget after listening to you complain so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going by your half-hearted replies, I thought you weren't listening.{I thought you weren't listening with your half-hearted replies.}{Of course not. He was listening with his ears.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as always, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there an event today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or did you shave your beard because your high school girlfriend told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if any taxis would come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go a little further you'll reach the main street.{not sure if splitting this up actually helped at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier to find one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm moving next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting my job, too.{and getting married and becoming a housewife... meh}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although that's a little later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, my boyfriend is coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Best of luck to you, Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.21,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,"What should we do afterwards?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.49,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I didn't say anything stupid like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.70,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stay up too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:51.78,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going out with her just for the sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:57.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.38,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:15.28,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is it that big of a deal to fall in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:27.74,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is true love something you can brag about?{"yearning" sounds incomplete without "for someone"}{idk, I just don't really like the word "yearning"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:17:01.59,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What does it mean "to love", anyway?{I'm afraid I've dumbed this down}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for suddenly barging in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The movie—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,let's go see another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you have to go home with me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
